summary:
Davos helping Jon prepare for the boat North
Davos: Ugh, this is so stupid, but okay, I will help you to not moon over Daenerys....
body:
Davos helping Jon prepare for the boat North

Davos: Ugh, this is so stupid, but okay, I will help you to not moon over Daenerys.

Jon: I need to think of unsexy, boring topics of conversation for this boat trip. I have some ideas.

Davos: Okay….

Jon: We could talk about ladders. We could talk about the various ways to skin a rabbit. And I could tell her about how to build a new latrine pit.

Davos: Oh! I have a good idea!

Jon: What?!

Davos: Why don’t you take your tunic off and show her your abs.
